Introduction

Yeonhee (연희) is a South Korean singer signed with Woollim Entertainment. She is the leader of the girl group Rocket Punch. She is also a member of the project girl group EL7Z UP.

She was introduced as one of the six members of Rocket Punch in a concept film that came out on July 23, 2019. Four days later, her individual concept film was revealed. She made her debut as the leader of Rocket Punch with the mini album "Pink Punch" on August 7, 2019.

On April 24, 2023, she participated in the survival show Queendom Puzzle and finished in 6th place earning her spot in the project girl group EL7Z UP. They made their debut on September 14, 2023, with their first mini album “7+Up”.
